---

<section
  data-test="cta-section"
  class="py-24 px-4 bg-indigo-600 dark:bg-indigo-700"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      Ready to build from a real spec?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-indigo-100 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      RootSpec is free and open source. Add it to your Claude project and start building better software today.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-indigo-600 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        ⭐ Star on GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/50 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        View Demo Projects ↗
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
